        "question": "设 $m$ 为实数，向量 $\\vec{a} = (1 + 2^{m}, 1 - 2^{m}), \\vec{b} = (4^{m} - 3, 4^{m} + 5)$，则数量积 $\\vec{a}\\cdot \\vec{b}$ 的最小值为______。",
        "solution": [
            "设 $t = 2^{m}$，则 $\\vec{a} = (1 + t, 1 - t), \\vec{b} = (t^{2} - 3, t^{2} + 5)$",
            "故 $\\vec{a}\\cdot \\vec{b} = (1 + t)(t^{2} - 3) + (1 - t)(t^{2} + 5) = 2(t - 2)^{2} - 6 \\geq -6$",
            "当 $t = 2$，即 $m = 1$ 时，$\\vec{a}\\cdot \\vec{b}$ 取到最小值 $-6$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["-6"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Numerical",
