        "id": 20210108,
        "subfield": "Optimization",
        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A1卷一试",
        "question": "正实数 $x, y$ 满足如下条件：存在 $a\\in [0,x], b\\in [0,y]$，使得 $a^{2} + y^{2} = 2, b^{2} + x^{2} = 1, ax + by = 1$，则 $x + y$ 的最大值为______。<img_d88e1d0e4c4e3dd53c7dbaefc806caef76a8a138f877b0a1518dff1e584ddd9d>",
        "solution": [
            "对于满足条件的正实数对 $(x,y)$，在平面直角坐标系 $xOy$ 中取点 $L(x,0), M(x,y), N(0,y)$，则四边形OLMN为矩形，点 $P(x,b), Q(a,y)$ 分别在边 $LM, MN$ 上",
            "由于 $a^{2} + y^{2} = 2$，$b^{2} + x^{2} = 1$，$ax + by = 1$，故",
            "$|OP| = \\sqrt{x^{2} + b^{2}} = 1, |OQ| = \\sqrt{a^{2} + y^{2}} = \\sqrt{2}$",
            "$|PQ| = \\sqrt{(a - x)^{2} + (b - y)^{2}} = \\sqrt{(a^{2} + y^{2}) + (b^{2} + x^{2}) - 2(ax + by)} = 1$",
            "从而 $\\triangle OPQ$ 是以 $P$ 为直角顶点的等腰直角三角形",
            "于是可设 $\\angle LOP = \\theta$，$\\angle QON = \\frac{\\pi}{4} - \\theta$，其中 $0 \\leq \\theta \\leq \\frac{\\pi}{4}$",
            "则 $x + y = |OL| + |ON| = |OP| \\cdot \\cos \\angle LOP + |OQ| \\cdot \\cos \\angle QON$",
            "$= \\cos \\theta + \\sqrt{2}\\cos(\\frac{\\pi}{4} - \\theta) = 2\\cos \\theta + \\sin \\theta$",
            "当 $\\theta = \\arctan \\frac{1}{2}$（相应有 $x = \\frac{2\\sqrt{5}}{5}, y = \\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}$）时，$x + y$ 取到最大值 $\\sqrt{5}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\sqrt{5}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
