        "id": 20210111,
        "subfield": "Analytic Geometry",
        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A1卷解答题",
        "question": "如图所示，在平面直角坐标系中，椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^{2}}{2} + y^{2} = 1$ 的左、右焦点分别为 $F_{1}, F_{2}$，设 $P$ 是第一象限内 $\\Gamma$ 上一点，$PF_{1}, PF_{2}$ 的延长线分别交 $\\Gamma$ 于点 $Q_{1}, Q_{2}$。设 $r_{1}, r_{2}$ 分别为 $\\triangle PF_{1}Q_{2}$，$\\triangle PF_{2}Q_{1}$ 的内切圆半径。求 $r_{1} - r_{2}$ 的最大值。<img_db4322033e157520ac1b1ee66d4921c86887faad909f9d9f88cf9361c3932e77>",
        "solution": [
            "易知 $F_{1}(-1, 0), F_{2}(1, 0)$",
            "设 $P(x_{0}, y_{0}), Q_{1}(x_{1}, y_{1}), Q_{2}(x_{2}, y_{2})$，由条件知 $x_{0}, y_{0} > 0, y_{1} < 0, y_{2} < 0$",
            "由椭圆定义得 $|PF_{1}| + |PF_{2}| = |Q_{1}F_{1}| + |Q_{1}F_{2}| = |Q_{2}F_{1}| + |Q_{2}F_{2}| = 2\\sqrt{2}$，故 $\\triangle PF_{1}Q_{2}$ 与 $\\triangle PF_{2}Q_{1}$ 的周长均为 $l = 4\\sqrt{2}$",
            "又 $|F_{1}F_{2}| = 2$，因此",
            "$r_{1} = \\frac{2S_{\\triangle PF_{1}Q_{2}}}{l} = \\frac{(y_{0} - y_{2}) \\cdot |F_{1}F_{2}|}{l} = \\frac{y_{0} - y_{2}}{2\\sqrt{2}}$",
            "同理得 $r_{2} = \\frac{y_{0} - y_{1}}{2\\sqrt{2}}$，所以 $r_{1} - r_{2} = \\frac{y_{1} - y_{2}}{2\\sqrt{2}}$",
            "以下先求 $y_{1} - y_{2}$",
            "直线 $PF_{1}$ 的方程为 $x = \\frac{(x_{0} + 1)y}{y_{0}} - 1$，将其代入 $\\frac{x^{2}}{2} + y^{2} = 1$ 并整理得",
            "$(\\frac{(x_{0} + 1)^{2}}{2y_{0}^{2}} + 1)y^{2} - \\frac{x_{0} + 1}{y_{0}}y - \\frac{1}{2} = 0$",
            "两边乘以 $2y_{0}^{2}$，并注意到 $x_{0}^{2} + 2y_{0}^{2} = 2$，可知",
            "$(3 + 2x_{0})y^{2} - 2(x_{0} + 1)y_{0}y - y_{0}^{2} = 0$",
            "该方程的两根为 $y_{0}, y_{1}$，由韦达定理得 $y_{0}y_{1} = -\\frac{y_{0}^{2}}{3 + 2x_{0}}$，于是 $y_{1} = -\\frac{y_{0}}{3 + 2x_{0}}$",
            "同理可得 $y_{2} = -\\frac{y_{0}}{3 - 2x_{0}}$，因此",
            "$y_{1} - y_{2} = \\frac{y_{0}}{3 - 2x_{0}} - \\frac{y_{0}}{3 + 2x_{0}} = \\frac{4x_{0}y_{0}}{9 - 4x_{0}^{2}}$",
            "由于 $9 - 4x_{0}^{2} = \\frac{1}{2}x_{0}^{2} + 9y_{0}^{2} \\geq 2\\sqrt{\\frac{1}{2}x_{0}^{2} \\cdot 9y_{0}^{2}} = 3\\sqrt{2}x_{0}y_{0}$",
            "故 $r_{1} - r_{2} = \\frac{y_{1} - y_{2}}{2\\sqrt{2}} = \\frac{\\sqrt{2}x_{0}y_{0}}{9 - 4x_{0}^{2}} \\leq \\frac{\\sqrt{2}x_{0}y_{0}}{3\\sqrt{2}x_{0}y_{0}} = \\frac{1}{3}$",
            "其中，等号成立时要求 $\\frac{1}{2}x_{0}^{2} = 9y_{0}^{2}$，相应地有 $x_{0} = \\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}, y_{0} = \\frac{\\sqrt{10}}{10}$",
            "所以 $r_{1} - r_{2}$ 的最大值为 $\\frac{1}{3}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{1}{3}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
